{"sgc":false,"sfy":false,"qfy":false,"transUser":{"id":9986082,"status":99,"demand":1,"userid":318830649,"nickname":"我有太多为什么","uptime":1589360381289},"lyricUser":{"id":5984996,"status":99,"demand":0,"userid":380889492,"nickname":"lovzeros","uptime":1581918606304},"lrc":{"version":6,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"编曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Ed Barrios\"}]}\n{\"t\":1000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"制作人: \"},{\"tx\":\"mixed matches\"}]}\n{\"t\":2000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Ed Barrios\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Pierre Thevenot\"}]}\n{\"t\":3000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Ed Barrios\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Pierre Thevenot\"}]}\n[00:08.091] Just take\n[00:11.376] Just take it\n[00:12.988] With how you want to live\n[00:16.302] And it's subtle in the moment when you want to begin\n[00:23.019] And you told me\n[00:24.668] That everything is just stupid, and\n[00:29.567] I can’t see it all when it goes to give\n[00:34.773] Well why would you try to make me see that everything is happening?\n[00:40.795] And I can't seem to keep it all under our feet\n[00:46.766] How would you know what else to say when I don't think I’ll ever change\n[00:53.092] When I can't seem to keep it all under our feet\n[00:58.645] Because maybe I can't find a reason to feel whole then\n[01:07.871] When I feel lonely\n[01:10.942] Say what you want of me\n[01:13.961] Because I just want to be safe and sound\n[01:17.035] You got me in a corner, I don't want to say goodbye\n[01:22.223] As long as I remember, I won't cave\n[01:28.143] Because you have the nerve to say I changed\n[01:34.213] And you look to trade me, I won't let you, I won't gut the seer\n[01:40.237] You're out of touch with everything, won’t you be honest with me\n[01:46.212] Well why would you want to make me see that everything is happening?\n[01:52.326] And I can’t seem to keep it all under our feet\n[01:58.060] How would you know what else to say when I don't think I’ll ever change\n[02:04.269] When I can't seem to keep it all under our feet\n[02:09.748] Because maybe I can't find a reason to feel whole then\n[02:18.814] When I feel lonely\n"},"klyric":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"tlyric":{"version":4,"lyric":"[by:我有太多为什么]\n[00:08.091]那就带走\n[00:11.376]将糟糕的情绪带走\n[00:12.988]伴着你想如何活着\n[00:16.302]当你想要开始时它是难以言说的\n[00:23.019]你向我倾诉\n[00:24.668]一切都让你感到麻木，以至于\n[00:29.567]我不能看到她就对她倾尽所有\n[00:34.773]你为什么要让我知道发生的那每一件事情\n[00:40.795]我似乎不能把这一切掌控住\n[00:46.766]我想我永远都不会改变 那你还会说些什么呢\n[00:53.092]当我似乎感觉不能控制住那一切的时候\n[00:58.645]那是可能我找不到一个理由感到完整\n[01:07.871]当我感到孤独的那一刻\n[01:10.942]说吧，你想从我这知道些什么呢\n[01:13.961]因为我只想要安稳和那一切的完好\n[01:17.035]你让我陷入了困境，我不想再去说再见\n[01:22.223]只要我还记得那些事，我就不会让步\n[01:28.143]你鼓足勇气说我不是以前的我\n[01:34.213]你想和我做交易，我不会同意你这么做的，我不想洞察先知\n[01:40.237]你什么都不了解，还对我虚与委蛇\n[01:46.212]你为什么要让我知道发生的那每一件事情\n[01:52.326]我也似乎不能控制住那一切\n[01:58.060]我想我永远不会改变，那你还会对我说些什么呢\n[02:04.269]当我似乎感觉不能控制住那一切的时候\n[02:09.748]那是可能我找不到一个理由能感受到像以前的完整\n[02:18.814]当我感到孤独的那一刻\n"},"romalrc":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"yrc":{"version":3,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"编曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Ed Barrios\"}]}\n{\"t\":1000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"制作人: \"},{\"tx\":\"mixed matches\"}]}\n{\"t\":2000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Ed Barrios\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Pierre Thevenot\"}]}\n{\"t\":3000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Ed Barrios\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Pierre Thevenot\"}]}\n[9810,1620](9810,1440,0)Just (11250,180,0)take\n[11430,1680](11430,240,0)Just (11670,420,0)take (12090,1020,0)it\n[13410,2700](13410,210,0)With (13620,180,0)how (13800,210,0)you (14010,360,0)want (14370,180,0)to (14550,1560,0)live\n[17070,5820](17070,270,0)And (17340,120,0)it's (17460,990,0)subtle (18450,270,0)in (18720,150,0)the (18870,930,0)moment (19800,300,0)when (20100,510,0)you (20610,450,0)want (21060,360,0)to (21420,1470,0)begin\n[22890,2280](22890,300,0)And (23190,180,0)you (23370,480,0)told (23850,1320,0)me\n[25200,4260](25200,360,0)That (25560,780,0)everything (26340,570,0)is (26910,420,0)just (27330,2040,0)stupid(29370,0,0), (29370,90,0)and\n[29490,4410](29490,